lead_paragraph: With every Eddie Jones victory, former England coach Stuart Lancaster must be thinking 'Hang on a minute, that was my idea' and could be forgiven a wry smile when he saw the team to play South Africa at Twickenham on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Robshaw, Wood and Vunipola Back in Harness for England
